# 08.04 Plugin Economy

## Overview

The Plugin Economy defines how cmdOS creates an open ecosystem where developers can build, distribute, and monetize extensions for the AI Execution Operating System.

Plugins allow cmdOS to continuously expand beyond its core capabilities by enabling external developers to create specialized solutions.

Core principle:

Developer

↓

Plugin Creation

↓

Marketplace Distribution

↓

User Adoption

↓

Economic Value

---

# 1. Plugin Economy Purpose

The purpose of the Plugin Economy is to create a sustainable ecosystem around cmdOS extensions.

It enables:

- Developer participation
- Capability expansion
- Marketplace growth
- Revenue sharing
- Ecosystem innovation

