# 4. Plugin Types

cmdOS supports multiple plugin categories.

---

# Capability Plugins

Purpose:

Add new execution abilities.

Examples:

- File management
- Data analysis
- External API integration

---

# Agent Plugins

Purpose:

Create specialized AI Agents.

Examples:

- Research Agent
- Trading Agent
- Business Agent
- Support Agent

---

# Integration Plugins

Purpose:

Connect external services.

Examples:

- CRM systems
- Communication platforms
- Cloud services

---

# Workflow Plugins

Purpose:

Provide ready-made automation workflows.

Examples:

- Business processes
- Productivity workflows
- Industry solutions

