# Summary

The Plugin Economy transforms cmdOS from a standalone AI system into an open AI execution ecosystem.

Developers create plugins.

Users access new capabilities.

Businesses deploy specialized solutions.

cmdOS provides the infrastructure connecting creation, distribution, and economic value.

The Plugin Economy becomes a key growth engine of the AI Execution Operating System.
